  {
    "key": "283fcd89ebeaa19f0cd44145198ce2e9bbecfdb58e31a53e4c628ffac8d8fe41",
    "original": "You dismissed ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"You dismissed \" + _event.m.Fired + \", a legend of the company\""
  },
  {
    "key": "10449e550db341d367eb1afbe0cc20b015f448b2b582c933983a5313b6c21dd5",
    "original": "[img]gfx/ui/events/event_64.png[/img]The man you let go wasn't just a part of the company: he was a legend. Many knew %dismissed%'s name, not just yourself and a few mercenaries, and having him leave is akin to firing a heroic general before a war-ending battle. The decision, naturally, does not go over well with the rest of the sellswords.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Text = \"[img]gfx/ui/events/event_64.png[/img]The man you let go wasn't just a part of the company: he was a legend. Many knew %dismissed%'s name, not just yourself and a few mercenaries, and having him leave is akin to firing a heroic general before a war-ending battle. The decision, naturally, does not go over well with the rest of the sellswords.\""
  }
